data.description: Wonderful 4 bedroom, 2 bath in Ashland Ranch! Fantastic community has playgrounds, baseball and soccer fields, volleyball and basketball courts, and more!! Lots of activities for everyone!! Grand entrance with soaring ceilings welcome you through the front door. HUGE Kitchen boasts maple cabinets, plant shelves, pantry, center island, and more. This split floorplan features both formal living and dining plus a spacious family room. Master suite has separate entrance outside, and a large bathroom suite with double sinks, separate shower and tub, plus HUGE walk-in closet. Plantation shutters, water softner, ceiling fans, & RV gate. Refrigerator, washer, and dryer to stay!! AZ room and low maintenance desert landscaping.
